entries.name: init
entries.text: Good evening. Do you need any sailing supplies?

children.name: hello
children.response: What brings you to these parts?

children.name: indeed
children.text: Indeed! Trying to save the world.

children.name: justWandering
children.text: Oh, nothing. Just seeing the sights.
children.response: Well you've come to the right place. Our little cove is wonderful. Be sure to meet some of the locals.

children.name: onSecondThought
children.text: On second thought, some shipping supplies sound good.
children.response: Wonderful! Feel free to poke around the chests and buckets, then ask me any questions you might have.
